271
00:23:01,110 --> 00:23:03,130
Do it again.

272
00:23:03,130 --> 00:23:06,870
You are so impressive!

273
00:23:07,680 --> 00:23:09,260
Is that all right?

274
00:23:12,220 --> 00:23:16,200
Don't you think Paris is such a romantic city?

275
00:23:16,760 --> 00:23:19,750
The romance people picture in their head

276
00:23:19,750 --> 00:23:21,640
is all here.

277
00:23:22,110 --> 00:23:24,310
Do you like Paris?

278
00:23:26,760 --> 00:23:29,670
I do, but also don't.

279
00:23:30,520 --> 00:23:32,800
When do you like it?

280
00:23:32,800 --> 00:23:35,180
Just like what Hemingway said,

281
00:23:35,180 --> 00:23:38,660
"If you're fortunate enough to stay in Paris when you are young,

282
00:23:38,660 --> 00:23:40,420
then for the rest of your life,

283
00:23:40,420 --> 00:23:42,650
no matter where you go,

284
00:23:42,650 --> 00:23:44,560
it will always be with you,

285
00:23:44,560 --> 00:23:48,360
because it is a moveable feast."

286
00:23:49,430 --> 00:23:51,640
When do you not like it?

287
00:24:01,460 --> 00:24:04,570
When you are not by my side.

288
00:24:07,790 --> 00:24:09,930
What's wrong?

289
00:24:11,850 --> 00:24:14,320
Every time I see...

290
00:24:14,320 --> 00:24:18,240
those beautiful buildings, I want to tell you.

291
00:24:18,240 --> 00:24:21,150
When I see young girls reading

292
00:24:21,150 --> 00:24:23,190
their love letters in the subway,

293
00:24:23,190 --> 00:24:25,210
I also want to tell you.

294
00:24:25,210 --> 00:24:27,940
Everything that happens around me,

295
00:24:27,940 --> 00:24:31,010
I want to tell you no matter when and where I am.

296
00:24:32,090 --> 00:24:36,360
Do you think I'm too immature?

297
00:24:42,700 --> 00:24:45,030
I'm actually just like you.

298
00:24:47,070 --> 00:24:48,880
Mo Fei...

299
00:24:55,110 --> 00:24:56,780
What?

300
00:24:59,160 --> 00:25:00,690
Never mind.

301
00:25:03,370 --> 00:25:06,580
I will come and pick you up after class tomorrow.

302
00:25:06,580 --> 00:25:08,660
Let's...

303
00:25:08,660 --> 00:25:10,400
