304
00:25:10,400 --> 00:25:12,850
Aren't we on a date right now?

305
00:25:12,850 --> 00:25:15,190
Right now is not the same.

306
00:25:15,190 --> 00:25:17,420
Tomorrow is more meaningful.

307
00:25:31,960 --> 00:25:34,290
Do you have coins?

308
00:25:34,290 --> 00:25:35,740
Why do you want coins?

309
00:25:35,740 --> 00:25:37,940
I want to make a wish.

310
00:26:07,040 --> 00:26:08,880
What did you wish for?

311
00:26:10,930 --> 00:26:14,600
The wish I made is for this rain to quickly end.

312
00:26:14,600 --> 00:26:17,050
Otherwise, it would be so unromantic today.

313
00:26:18,150 --> 00:26:20,360
