332
00:27:20,340 --> 00:27:23,770
When you work hard for a whole day and get back home,

333
00:27:24,940 --> 00:27:28,320
you will feel very happy to see the other person's

334
00:27:28,320 --> 00:27:30,760
car parked in the garage...

335
00:27:32,200 --> 00:27:34,630
and want to spend the rest of your life with them.

336
00:27:36,490 --> 00:27:38,500
So I want to ask you,

337
00:27:39,670 --> 00:27:44,520
if you work hard for a whole day and see my car parked in the garage when you get home,

338
00:27:46,100 --> 00:27:48,760
