340
00:28:08,860 --> 00:28:12,820
Looks like the wish I made came true. The rain stopped.

341
00:28:13,430 --> 00:28:15,530
Heaven has really given me some face.

342
00:28:17,910 --> 00:28:19,670
So?

343
00:28:24,770 --> 00:28:26,940
I want to love you...

344
