It's quite a challenge.

422
00:35:48,150 --> 00:35:50,310
Don't be mad, okay?

423
00:35:50,310 --> 00:35:53,680
I don't want that, either.

424
00:35:53,680 --> 00:35:57,440
But you know it's a rare opportunity.

425
00:36:00,380 --> 00:36:01,660
What?

426
00:36:01,660 --> 00:36:02,940
