442
00:36:52,670 --> 00:36:54,950
- Then when will we have kids?
- What?

443
00:37:18,820 --> 00:37:19,930
Morning, Brother Xuan.

444
00:37:19,930 --> 00:37:21,620
Morning.

445
00:37:25,210 --> 00:37:28,550
Today, I'm prepared to give Mo Fei a...

446
00:37:29,350 --> 00:37:30,950
a surprise.

447
00:37:30,950 --> 00:37:33,930
Really? What kind of surprise?

448
00:37:34,950 --> 00:37:36,680
Are you curious?

449
00:37:36,680 --> 00:37:40,480
Forget it. If you don't want to tell me, forget it then.

450
00:37:57,020 --> 00:38:00,320
- Yes, yes.
- This one looks nice.

451
00:38:00,320 --> 00:38:02,290
This one as well. These.

452
00:38:02,290 --> 00:38:04,890
Mo Fei, you are married?

453
00:38:04,890 --> 00:38:06,410
Yes.

454
00:38:06,410 --> 00:38:10,130
Mo Fei is married.

455
00:38:10,130 --> 00:38:11,960
What does your husband do?

456
00:38:11,960 --> 00:38:13,290
Is he handsome?

457
00:38:13,290 --> 00:38:15,430
Mo Fei is so pretty.

458
00:38:15,430 --> 00:38:17,550
Her husband can't be bad, right?

459
00:38:17,550 --> 00:38:21,520
- Show us a picture of him!
 - That's right. Show us his picture.

460
00:38:21,520 --> 00:38:25,830
