464
00:38:38,740 --> 00:38:41,730
I'm here to see Mo Fei.

465
00:38:41,730 --> 00:38:45,050
I don't have to look. He's here.

466
00:38:45,050 --> 00:38:47,680
Mo Fei, your husband is so handsome.

467
00:38:47,680 --> 00:38:49,700
Why were you so embarassed?

468
00:38:49,700 --> 00:38:51,920
- How is he so handsome?
- Exactly.

469
00:38:51,920 --> 00:38:53,790
We'll get going then.

470
00:38:53,790 --> 00:38:56,050
Let's go.

471
00:38:56,050 --> 00:38:57,610
Hello.

472
00:39:05,210 --> 00:39:07,030
What?

473
00:39:07,030 --> 00:39:10,510
Others have bear hugs. Why is it like this when it comes to me?

474
00:39:10,510 --> 00:39:12,020
You are so heavy. How can I do a bear hug?

475
00:39:12,020 --> 00:39:14,160
How am I heavy? I'm very light.

476
00:39:14,160 --> 00:39:15,850
Come on, come on. Let's do a bear hug.

477
00:39:15,850 --> 00:39:18,120
- No!
- Let's do it again.

478
00:39:18,120 --> 00:39:19,600
Again.

479
00:39:19,600 --> 00:39:22,520
- Come. One, two—
- Hold me.

480
00:39:25,130 --> 00:39:27,980
- You didn't make it.
- I did.

481
00:39:28,530 --> 00:39:31,390
What are you doing here? Did you miss me?

482
00:39:32,440 --> 00:39:35,490
What? Why are you shaking your head?

483
00:39:35,490 --> 00:39:37,230
I'm here to ask for directions.

484
00:39:37,230 --> 00:39:40,490
Ask for directions? Don't you know how to use the GPS?

485
00:39:40,490 --> 00:39:41,610
If you miss me, just say it.

486
00:39:41,610 --> 00:39:44,640
GPS can't find the place I'm looking for.

487
00:39:44,640 --> 00:39:46,640
It's the road to your heart.

488
00:39:47,620 --> 00:39:50,990
Where did you learn that?

489
00:39:52,790 --> 00:39:53,690
I missed you.

490
00:39:53,690 --> 00:39:55,790
I missed you, too.

491
00:39:55,790 --> 00:40:00,520
What are you doing? Let me sleep in for a bit more.

492
