497
00:40:18,580 --> 00:40:20,960
Don't mess with me.

498
00:40:20,960 --> 00:40:23,190
Your career is on the rise right now.

499
00:40:23,190 --> 00:40:27,260
As your manager, of course, I have to push you to progress. Here, drink up.

