00:40:36,570 --> 00:40:40,300
Isn't my work for today scheduled for tonight? Why did you wake me up so early?

502
00:40:40,300 --> 00:40:43,030
I met someone behind the stage.

503
00:40:43,030 --> 00:40:45,490
He is a producer. He's produced quite a few works.

